description:
Sportsdoctors, the main partner of SDC Co., Ltd. is an NGO supporting domestic and foreign medical aid with 3,300 general hospitals and 1 million partner physicians in Korea, and after it was officially registered in UN DPI in 2003, Sportsdoctors has provided medical aid over 3,000 times in Korea and overseas.

SDCOIN is a life-saving coin sponsored by Sportsdoctors and developed by SDC Co., Ltd. by using blockchain to build a global medical business with a medical coin network and generating stable profits so that these profits can be used for the “Save Lives in the Global Community,” a medical contribution project.
name: SDCOIN
